{"tid":1367180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本電視節目 一圖解釋元朗恐襲事件","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T08:05:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e2febdc1a84b196d5d2bd53e33c5747057d263b0","tid":1367180,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/jp_U8xF1_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjp_U8xF1_1200x0.png&h=d6324bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n名為「スッキリ（《爽快早晨》）」的節目播放圖像顯示，中國政府即中國共產黨對出動解放軍有顧慮（圖片來源：Twitter）<br />\n<br />\n「日本電視台」一個資訊節目今早提到元朗暴力毆打市民事件。節目引述一名評論員的說法，以圖像直指，中國政府與香港政府聘請「黑社會」的白衫集團，毆打示威者。<br />\n<br />\n名為「スッキリ（《爽快早晨》）」的節目播放圖像顯示，中國政府即中國共產黨對出動解放軍有顧慮；加上香港政府難以用警察鎮壓示威，因此兩地政府聯手聘請來自三合會的白衫團體，向示威者示襲。<br />\n<br />\n節目播放的圖像資料來自日本知名評論家石平。生於 1962 年的石平（現名石平太郎）是中國人，生於四川，畢業於北京大學、神戶大學。他早年深受文化大革命迫害，1982 年開始參加中國民主運動，1989 年天安門事件後，由於對中國政府失望，歸化日本，為日本《產經新聞》專欄「石平的 China Watch」執筆。在日本，他曾多次對中國作出批判。<br />\n<br />\n日本電視台節目「スッキリ（Sukkiri，「痛快」的意思）」於 2006 年首播，現逢周一至五在 8 點至 10 點 25 分播出，主持為加藤浩次、近藤春菜和水卜麻美。簡稱「日視（日テレ，Nittele）」的日本電視台，則是以日本關東廣域圈為播放區域的無線電視台，也是日本第一家商業電視台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%97%A5%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%AE%B6-%E7%9B%B4%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%83%B1%E9%BB%91%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%89%93%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2583%25B1%25E9%25BB%2591%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%2F&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b04ecf68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2583%25B1%25E9%25BB%2591%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%2F&h=ce53801c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%97%A5%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%AE%B6-%E7%9B%B4%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%83%B1%E9%BB%91%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%89%93%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85/</a>"},{"pid":"a905ec4f1e03af60e35898856bc32c83838561f9","tid":1367180,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"デモ隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392a9058862376889972e5f6270d0397607d113a","tid":1367180,"uid":38030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"如果表達埋無差別襲擊就完美"},{"pid":"456f702207400b554a03539d03ec51f7cc49525f","tid":1367180,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0035eafcf1da10d999ff073eb255a2e8fe08e28b","tid":1367180,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vF1klTk7rKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvF1klTk7rKs&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=e0a896c4\" target=\"_b